Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.00,0:04:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,700)}그렇긴 한가...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.63,0:04:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,700)}그러긴 뭐가요!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.25,0:04:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,700)}진짜로...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.94,0:04:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,700)}막 울기 시작하나\N싶더니만
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.60,0:04:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,700)\fad(00,00)}갑자기 흥을 타더니\N삼바를 추고 그런다니까요?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.91,0:04:49.55,Default - Left,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,600)\fna두리둥실\pos(1150,475)\fscy70\t(00,150,\fscy200)\t(150,250,\fscy80)\t(250,350,\fscy100)}또르틸라~!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.25,0:04:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,700)\fad(00,00)}그건 좀\N미친 거 같은데...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.14,0:04:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,평소랑 똑같은 봇치...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.33,0:04:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,아니에요~!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.60,0:04:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,얌마들아~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.17,0:04:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,잠깐 와서
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.02,0:04:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,봇치쨩이 저거 좀 못하게\N해주면 안 되냐?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.88,0:04:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,저거?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.23,0:05:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,아침부터\N저 상태로
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.15,0:05:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,라이브 하우스 앞에
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.37,0:05:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,매미 무덤을\N계속 만들고 있더라니까~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.98,0:05:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,상태 너무 심각하잖아!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.39,0:05:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,왜 정신줄\N놔버린 거야!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.93,0:05:17.21,Centor - Left,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,1000)\fna태백산맥\b0\fs60\blur4\c&H000000&\3c&HBC29A3&\pos(1074.667,460)}잘 가…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.10,0:05:17.21,Centor - Left,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,1000)\fna태백산맥\b0\fs60\blur4\c&H000000&\3c&HBC29A3&\pos(1093.333,572)}잘 가…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.39,0:05:17.21,Centor - Left,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,1000)\fna태백산맥\b0\fs60\blur4\c&H000000&\3c&HBC29A3&\pos(1162.667,660)}잘 가…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.29,0:05:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,여름방학이 오늘로 끝나서\N그런 걸까요...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.16,0:05:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,신학기는\N나도 싫어
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.06,0:05:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,그보다 말야
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.46,0:05:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,너희, 이번 여름에\N어디 놀러 가자고 해주긴 했어?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.88,0:05:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,에...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.72,0:05:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,어쩌다\N요전에 알바할 때
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.72,0:05:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,방학에 뭐 하냐는\N얘기가 나왔는데―
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.05,0:05:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5}봇치쨩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.23,0:05:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5}여름방학에\N알바 없는 날에는 뭐 해?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.73,0:05:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5}어...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.16,0:05:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5}어, 저기...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.93,0:05:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5}도..동생이 기타\N가르쳐달라고 해서...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.98,0:05:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5}가르쳐주고\N그랬어요...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.54,0:05:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5}헤에~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.45,0:05:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5}멋지네
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.25,0:05:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,600)\blur5}그..그런데...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.80,0:05:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,00)\blur5\fna두리둥실\bord5\3c&H950BE6&}오늘은 언니한테\N기타를 배웠습니다!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.59,0:05:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\fna두리둥실\bord5\3c&H950BE6&}언니는\N언제나 집에 있어서
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.74,0:05:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\fna두리둥실\bord5\3c&H950BE6&}기타를 연습해서
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.17,0:05:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\fna두리둥실\bord5\3c&H950BE6&}굉장하다고\N생각했습니다!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.54,0:05:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\fna두리둥실\bord5\3c&H950BE6&}후타리는 여름방학에\N할 게 잔뜩 있는데다
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.31,0:05:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\fna두리둥실\bord5\3c&H950BE6&}친구랑도\N놀아야 하니까…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.80,0:05:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\fna두리둥실\bord5\3c&H950BE6&}언니처럼\N매일 연습 못하니까
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.73,0:06:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\fna두리둥실\bord5\3c&H950BE6&}굉장하다고\N생각했습니다!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.08,0:06:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5}도..동생의 발언에 대해\N고민에 빠져버려서...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.20,0:06:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5}며칠간\N앓아누웠습니다...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.12,0:06:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5}그러니...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.05,0:06:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5}예정은\N비워뒀어요!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.59,0:06:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5}뭐...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.08,0:06:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5}어..없는 게 아니라\N비워둔 거라구요!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.10,0:06:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5}어, 그러냐...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.00,0:06:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,그러던데?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.87,0:06:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,그걸 좀 더 빨리\N알려줬어야지!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.24,0:06:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,놀러 가자고\N불러보려고는 했는데요...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.94,0:06:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,여기 오는 날 말고는\N전부 예정이 차 있어서...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.97,0:06:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,모르는 애들이 있으면\N고토 씨가 위축되지 않을까 싶고...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.68,0:06:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,이지치 선배는요...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.14,0:06:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,어, 나는...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.59,0:06:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,연습 날 말고는\N집 정리하거나...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.21,0:06:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,여기서\N알바 했었으니까...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.08,0:06:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,료..료 선배는...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.23,0:06:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,너희가 알아서\N불러냈을 줄 알았지
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.50,0:06:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,어...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.21,0:06:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,그럼, 그 말은...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.52,0:06:47.29,Default - Left,,0,0,0,,{\pos(715,980)}-아무도 봇치쨩이랑\N\h놀아주지 않았다...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.29,0:06:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,너희 그냥\N밴드 이름 바꿔라...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.97,0:06:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(961.18,980.8)}고...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.01,0:06:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960.64,979.36)}고...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.05,0:06:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(958.46,978.22)}고...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.09,0:06:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(961.9,979.1)}고...!
