Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.39,0:06:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,980.76)}고, 고, 고...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.43,0:06:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(959.16,981.52)}고, 고, 고...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.47,0:06:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(961.36,978.04)}고, 고, 고...!
