Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.17,0:06:57.23,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,10)\fn양재둘기체M\fs50\bord5\pos(445,285)}도코사헥사엔산…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.05,0:06:57.23,Default - Left,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,10)\fn양재둘기체M\fs50\bord5\pos(650,425)}에이코\N사펜타엔산…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.10,0:06:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,제발 돌아와~!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.73,0:06:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,그렇지...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.75,0:07:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,다 같이 지금부터\N바다에 가자구!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.26,0:07:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,에노시마라든가!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.33,0:07:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,괜찮겠네~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.41,0:07:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,시모키타에서 출발하면\N갈아탈 필요도 없고!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.91,0:07:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,그..그래도...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.46,0:07:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,오 늘 연 습 은\N어 쩔 끈 데 요...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.10,0:07:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,말투 왜 박살남?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.43,0:07:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,딱히 연습이라면\N언제든 할 수 있잖아!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.88,0:07:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,다음 라이브도\N아직 안 정해졌고 말야~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.29,0:07:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,다 같이 여름방학\N마지막 추억 만들기 하자!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.87,0:07:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,추억...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.12,0:07:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,어때?\N괜찮지?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.30,0:07:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,다 같이\N바다에 가요!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.63,0:07:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,하지만 시기적으로\N이제 헤엄은 못 칠 거 같다
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.85,0:07:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,으으...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.61,0:07:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,헤 엄 도 못 치 는 데
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.80,0:07:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,바 다 가 는 의 미 없 죠...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.14,0:07:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,그..그래도 바다의 집은\N아직 있을 거야!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.84,0:07:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,멸치 덮밥 먹자!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.98,0:07:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,그리고 해변에서\N바다도 보고...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.30,0:07:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,바다...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.34,0:07:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,해변...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.52,0:07:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,1000)}어때~?\N상상만 해도 즐겁지~?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.20,0:07:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\fna두리둥실\fs70}기다려보라니깐~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.59,0:07:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\fna두리둥실\fs70}안 기다려~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.37,0:07:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,400)\fna두리둥실\fs70}꺄악…!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.95,0:08:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\fna두리둥실\fs70}여름도...\N곧 끝나는구나
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.62,0:08:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,600)\fna두리둥실\fs70}내년에도\N같이 오자?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.32,0:08:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\fn양재백두체b\b0}으헉…!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.76,0:08:21.29,Centor - Left,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,600)\fna두리둥실\b0\fs50\bord5\pos(980,730)}트로피컬 러브…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.85,0:08:21.29,Centor - Left,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,600)\fna두리둥실\b0\fs50\bord5\pos(1005,790)}뿨에블…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.64,0:08:18.50,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,600)\fna두리둥실\fs60\pos(770,440)}어어!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.09,0:08:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,고토 씨!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.89,0:08:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,왜 또\N이렇게 되는 거래니...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.33,0:08:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,왠지 결정타를\N때려버린 거 같은데요...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.87,0:08:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,으음~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.26,0:08:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,좋았어!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.03,0:08:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,또 폭주하기 전에\N서두르자!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.02,0:08:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,롸져!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.75,0:08:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,키타쨩!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.63,0:08:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,봇치쨩\N잘 부탁해~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.55,0:08:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,네...!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.10,0:08:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,좋았어~!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.76,0:08:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,그럼 에노시마로\N렛츠 고~!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.59,0:08:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,고~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.69,0:08:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,고토 씨!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.51,0:08:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,조금만 더 있으면\N여름의 추억이 생길 테니깐!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.15,0:08:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,조금만 더\N참으면 되니까!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.84,0:08:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,00)}무섭다…!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.04,0:08:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,트…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.66,0:08:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,1000)}트러삐까루…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.19,0:08:54.01,Default - A,,0,0,0,,여기는 블랙홀...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.37,0:08:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1610,435)\fad(300,00)\fna두리둥실\fs60}은하의 끝…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.57,0:09:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1610,435)\fad(00,600)\fna두리둥실\fs60}여름의 햇살도\N닿지 않는 곳…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.11,0:09:03.43,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.43,0:09:04.57,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.06,0:08:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,이 지경이 되다니...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.63,0:08:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,어지간히도\N학교가 싫나 보다...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.89,0:08:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,교칙이\N엄하기라도 해?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.58,0:08:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,아뇨...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.35,0:09:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,비교적 자유로운\N교풍이라고 생각하는데요
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.56,0:09:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,문화제 같은 때는\N엄청 떠들썩하구요!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.93,0:09:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,좋겠다~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.44,0:09:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,우리 학교는\N꽤 엄한 편이니까
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.17,0:09:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,문화제 같은 때도\N막 답답한 느낌이라구~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.88,0:09:18.70,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,10)\fna뉴궁서m\fs55\bord5\pos(465,315)\c&H1A1386&\3c&H9FDEFB&}꿀벌의 생태관찰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.88,0:09:18.70,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,10)\fna뉴궁서m\fs55\bord5\pos(1390,335)\c&H1A1386&\3c&H9FDEFB&}환경에 따른 갯지렁이의{\fs25}\N\N{\fs55}체중변화 조사
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.88,0:09:18.70,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,10)\fna뉴궁서m\fs30\bord5\c&H1A1386&\3c&H9FDEFB&\pos(465,545)}절지동물문 곤충강\N벌목 꿀벌과 꿀벌속\N학명 : Apis
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.88,0:09:18.70,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,10)\fna뉴궁서m\fs30\bord5\c&H1A1386&\3c&H9FDEFB&\pos(1350,550)}환형통물문 다모강\N부채발갯지렁이목 참갯지렁이과 참갯지렁이속\N학명 : Hediste
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.88,0:09:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,730)}포스터는 연구 성과\N전시같은 것밖에 없고!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.80,0:09:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,730)}그렇구나...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.75,0:09:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,730)}시모키타자와 고교는\N진학교니까요
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.92,0:09:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,그럼 두 분도\N머리 좋으신가봐요!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.51,0:09:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,아니~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.23,0:09:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,난 그냥 평범하구~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.02,0:09:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,료는...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.05,0:09:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,좀 그러지...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.06,0:09:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,에...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.90,0:09:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,저번 시험 때는\N전부 낙제점이었지~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.58,0:09:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,응
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.30,0:09:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,에에...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.14,0:09:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,나랑 같은 고등학교를\N고른 이유가
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.40,0:09:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,집에서 가까워서\N그런 거였으니깐~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.36,0:09:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,맞아
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.79,0:09:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,그래도...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.57,0:09:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,그럼 수험에는\N어떻게 합격하신 거예요...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.65,0:09:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,료는 완전히\N벼락치기 타입이니까
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.76,0:09:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,수험 전에는\N상당히 열심히 했는데
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.96,0:09:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,지금은 전부\N잊어버렸나 보더라구~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.49,0:09:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,공부 열심히 하면
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.98,0:09:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,베이스 치는 법을\N잊어버려
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.81,0:09:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,설마 료 선배는...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.46,0:09:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,800)}미스테리어스하고\N사려 깊은 게 아니라...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.06,0:09:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,하지 마~!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.85,0:09:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,뇌가 너무 작아서
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.78,0:10:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,머리 속에서 데굴거리는\N소리가 들려!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.37,0:10:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,이 소리,\N신곡에 쓸 수 있으려나?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.63,0:10:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,그만해!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.27,0:10:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,내 이미지를\N깨뜨리지 말아줘~!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.65,0:10:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,전철 안에서는\N조용히!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.48,0:10:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,방금 대화는\N기억에서 소거할래요~!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.21,0:10:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,사람은 사랑이 너무도 강하면\N이렇게 되어 가는 건가...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.52,0:10:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,시..시공간이 왜곡되는...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.84,0:10:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,그래서!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.38,0:10:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,봇치쨩한테는\N지금 뭐가 보이는 거니~?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.22,0:10:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,학교에서 혼자라는 게\N신기해
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.21,0:10:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,이렇게 재밌는데
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.76,0:10:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,그치~
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.66,0:10:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,봇치쨩이 실제로는\N굉장한 애라는 걸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.71,0:10:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,학교 애들도\N이해해주면 좋겠네~
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.51,0:10:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,신학기부터는 저도\N종종 만나러 가볼게요
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.05,0:10:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,꼭 좀 그래줘!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.73,0:10:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,봇치쨩의\N지금 꿈이
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.23,0:10:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,고교 중퇴니깐!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.80,0:10:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,그걸 꿈이라고 해도\N되는 거예요!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.91,0:10:42.28,Default - Left,,0,0,0,,{\fad(10,10)\fna천생연분\fs60\bord5\pos(920,500)\frx18\fry20\frz340\c&H503934&\3c&HBDAEA2&}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.51,0:10:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,아무튼~
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.51,0:10:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,오늘은 봇치쨩이랑\N즐거운 여름 추억을 만들자~!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.68,0:10:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,사진 찍자!\N고토 씨!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.62,0:10:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,그럼, 소금 소프트크림\N먹고 올 테니까
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.68,0:10:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,나중에 보자!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.26,0:10:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,인간아~
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.04,0:10:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,누가 자유행동\N해도 된댔어!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.82,0:10:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,고토 씨~\N슬슬 좀 일어나자...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.19,0:11:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,고토 씨~!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.31,0:11:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,웅구…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.73,0:11:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,와, 저기 봐!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.92,0:11:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,바다 넓다~!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.51,0:11:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,으어!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.66,0:11:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,어..어라?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.91,0:11:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,어..어느새!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.78,0:11:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,진짜 지금껏\N의식이 없었구나~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.27,0:11:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,고..고마워요, 키타 씨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.38,0:11:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,600)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}바다에 오는 게\N얼마만일까...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.21,0:11:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}막상 와보니까...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.85,0:11:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}역시 예뻐서 좋―
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.29,0:11:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs90}이봐, 우리 언니들~!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.68,0:11:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,끄아악…!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.27,0:11:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,한가하면 우리 바다의 집에서\N밥 먹고 가라구Yo~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.50,0:11:30.93,Default - A,,0,0,0,,귀여운 사람들한테는\N할인도 해준다구~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.93,0:11:32.17,Default - A,,0,0,0,,4명이니까\N자리도 금방 마련할 수 있어~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.55,0:11:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}시..실물...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.38,0:11:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}리얼 파티피플~!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.23,0:11:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,우리 언니들은 JK?\N어디서 왔어~?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.42,0:11:36.82,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,200)\fna두리둥실\t(00,100,\fscx120\fscy120)\t(100,200,\fscx200\fscy200)\t(200,400,\fscx220\fscy200)\pos(500,755)}빳!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.05,0:11:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,400)\fna두리둥실\fs60\fs70\fscy70\t(00,100,\fscy200)\t(100,200,\fscy80)\t(200,300,\fscy100)\pos(555,440)}힉!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.51,0:11:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,봇치쨩이\N폭발사산해버렸다!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.85,0:11:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,그림으로 그려낸 듯한\N'웨이족'이었어
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.91,0:11:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,저걸 상대하기에는\N상성이 너무 불리해~!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.65,0:11:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,600)}서둘러\N바다에서 떨어져요!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.06,0:11:52.10,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,10)\fna두리둥실\fs70\pos(1730,705)}웨이~!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.47,0:11:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,맛있게 드십쇼~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.89,0:11:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,자, 이건\N고토 씨 몫!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.88,0:11:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 감사합니다...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.65,0:12:04.20,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(10,10)\fna두리둥실\fs35\bord4\3c&H6100B7&\pos(1515,785)\frz7.808}에노시마 {\c&H6100B7&\bord0}통구이{\fs20}\N\N{\fna키즈\fs55}문어 전병
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.23,0:12:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,이건...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.28,0:12:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,문어 전병!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.70,0:12:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,문어를 1t의 힘으로\N찍어누르는 거래!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.86,0:12:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,1톤의 힘...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.36,0:12:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,마이따...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.05,0:12:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,나...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.09,0:12:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,맛있는 거 센서도\N끝내주지
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.12,0:12:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,여..역시 대단하세요!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.81,0:12:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,봇치쨩...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.81,0:12:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,아무튼 기운 차려서\N다행이야~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.13,0:12:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,이거, 크기도 크고\N귀여운 게!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.25,0:12:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,사진빨 잘 받겠네요!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.40,0:12:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,좋아!\N사진 찍자~!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.25,0:12:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,네~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.41,0:12:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,찍습니다~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.83,0:12:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,보여줘, 보여줘~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.99,0:12:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,완전\N좋은 느낌이에요!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.64,0:12:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}다 같이 먹은\N문어 전병...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.02,0:12:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}여름의 추억...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.29,0:12:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 오늘은...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.89,0:12:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,오늘은...\N정말 감사했습니다...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.47,0:12:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,수고 많으셨어요...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.67,0:12:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,왜 벌써 클라이막스에\N들어갔어!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.93,0:12:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,이리 하여...\N나의 여름은...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.10,0:12:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,600)}끝났다...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.74,0:12:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs90}이제부터\N시작이잖아!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.72,0:13:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,으아...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.67,0:13:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,1000)}으아아...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.93,0:13:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,좋았어~!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.99,0:13:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,여기서\N정상까지 올라가요~!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.97,0:13:13.14,Default - Right,,0,0,0,,{\fad(10,10)\fn@a편봉체\fs70\bord5\c&H3F4B49&\3c&HD9E4E0&\frx6\fry4\frz276.2\move(1450,580,1450,680,00,2170)}에노시마 신사
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.72,0:13:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,에...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.90,0:13:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,계단...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.56,0:13:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,스스로의 힘으로 올라가\N내려다보는 풍경만큼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.81,0:13:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,멋진 건 없다고\N생각하진 않으세요~?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.30,0:13:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,아니!\N그딴 건 필요 없어!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.32,0:13:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,열심히 해봐요!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.16,0:13:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,싫다!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.00,0:13:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,고토 씨도!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.98,0:13:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,아아, 으...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.37,0:13:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,이지치 선배는\N가능하시죠!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.50,0:13:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,나도 막 내키지는...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.87,0:13:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,으읇!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.49,0:13:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,키타쨩!!\N전에 없이 눈부셔!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.83,0:13:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,어..어째서!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.08,0:13:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,펴..펴...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.75,0:13:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,평소에는 억제되는 거 같던\N아우라가!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.74,0:13:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,해..햇빛을 쬐는 것으로~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.15,0:13:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,리미터 해제\N되고 있는 것인가...!
