Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.34,0:13:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(10,00)\fna두리둥실\fs120\bord6\fscx80\fscy50\t(00,160,\fscx200\fscy200)\pos(960,350)\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&HF087F3&}키
