Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.48,0:13:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,자, 어서 가자구요!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.53,0:13:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 하하...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.14,0:13:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,여러분~!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.16,0:13:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,얼른~!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.15,0:13:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,더는 무리...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.31,0:13:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,못 올라가...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.35,0:13:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,키타쨩하고\N점점 멀어져 간다...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.10,0:14:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,더는 못 가~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.83,0:14:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,풍경이고 나발이고\N알 게 뭐여...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.65,0:14:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,개나 주라 그래...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.73,0:14:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,두 분 다\N기운 좀 내세요!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.82,0:14:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,이제 막\N시작된 참이잖아요
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.99,0:14:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,일단 좀 쉬게 해줘~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.42,0:14:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,어쩔 수 없네요~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.17,0:14:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,600)}키타쨩은\N기운도 넘치는구나~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.52,0:14:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,에...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.25,0:14:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,에스카...?
